FOOT & MOUTH DISEASE, CATTLE - JAPAN
***********************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
See Also
Foot & mouth disease, new strain - Japan 20000512182550
Foot & mouth disease, confirmed - Japan 20000406234216
